Helix Workflow Kernel

The workflow kernel, schemas, scheduler, runtime adapters, tests, and examples
in this package were independently authored for Helix.

The architecture review considered Claude Code workflows, the Claude Agent
SDK, pi-dynamic-workflows implementations, and CLIProxyAPI as behavioral and
architectural references. No source or fixtures from the unlicensed
Michaelliv/pi-dynamic-workflows repository are included. No third-party
workflow package or proxy is bundled.
